  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div class=\"qti-layout-row\"> <div class=\"qti-layout-col12\"> <div class=\"prompt\"> <p class=\"dap_body\">Consecutive terms of a sequence have the values&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\"><semantics><mn>2</mn><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>,&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"negative 1\"><math alttext=\"negative 1\"><semantics><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>,&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"1 half\"><math alttext=\"1 half\"><semantics><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>,&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"negative 1 fourth\"><math alttext=\"negative 1 fourth\"><semantics><mrow><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>, and&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"1 over 8\"><math alttext=\"1 over 8\"><semantics><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>8</mn></mfrac><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>. Of the following, which describes the sequence?</p> </div> </div> </div>\n",
    "answer": "B-65378",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​​The terms could be part of a geometric sequence with a common ratio of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"negative 2\"><math alttext=\"negative 2\"><semantics><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>.</p>",
        "value": "A-65377"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​The terms could be part of a geometric sequence with a common ratio of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"negative 1 half\"><math alttext=\"negative 1 half\"><semantics><mrow><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>.</p>",
        "value": "B-65378"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​​The terms could be part of a geometric sequence with a common ratio of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"1 half\"><math alttext=\"1 half\"><semantics><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>.</p>",
        "value": "C-65379"
